:: ui
The {{{<<ui>>}}} macro can be used to control many features of SugarCube's default UI from within macro code.

<<link 'Toggle the UI Bar'>>
    <<ui 'toggle'>>
<</link>>

<<link 'Open the Saves Dialog'>>
    <<ui 'saves'>>
<</link>>

